## Summary
This documentation page provides an overview of Amplitude Activation, a self-service personalization platform that enables true one-to-one personalization without requiring data science or engineering resources. It explains how the platform uses cohorts, computations, predictions, recommendations, and various delivery methods (synchronizations and APIs) to help marketers target the right users with the right messages at the right time.

